rows.label: tlk20010151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My master thinks of me as if I were family...
He is a truly gentle person.

rows.label: tlk20010151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
However... he still isn't used to combat,
and it seems the sight of blood frightens him.

rows.label: tlk20010151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The line between kindness and weakness is a fine one.
I am resolved to do my utmost to support
my master in any way I can.
